Text: 500pop，食物  鹿  羊   石料   黄金    木材都是100000存量 ，  石墙是100000血量，圣殿骑士团 威尼斯商人 制造上限调整到300，所有文明村民只占用0.5人口。500pop, food, deer, sheep, stone, gold and wood all have a stock of 100,000, the stone wall has 100,000 health points, the production limit of the Knights Templar and Venetian merchants has been adjusted to 300, and all civilized villagers only occupy 0.5 population.
